data.description: Location! Location! Beautiful House and very spacious 4 nice size Bedrooms plus two full bathrooms. Large master bedroom with plenty of closet space, clean and very well maintain property. Move in Ready.  The house has partial wooden floors, laminated and title, Ample drive way, water softener filter fully paid! surveillance cameras included. Nice floor plan!  Located in the heart in L.A. Walking distance to USC UNIVERSITY, COLISEUM, BANC OF CALIFORNIA STADIUM AND FREEWAYS, SHOPPING CENTERS, SCHOOLS AND MUCH MORE. THIS IS A MUST SEE!
